Class CarExample

    java.lang.Object
    java.awt.Component
    CarExample
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.util.EventListener, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.event.KeyListener, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable
public class CarExample
extends java.awt.Component
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.event.KeyListener

Basic JADE simulator with a 2 wheeled cart travelling through a 2D "platform environment". An almost direct port of the CarExample program in the original FLADE 0.6 alpha release (2005-11-20). Features include:

  • 2 wheeled cart with suspension
  • double-jointed pendulum mass in the middle of the car
  • "One-way" ramp (car can come up through toggleLine but can't go down through it)
